  "gwSpecs": {
    "description": "The Jet Wash7 is a compact and fast LED moving wash light with motorized zoom control.\nThe 20W Osram RGBW LED source provides plenty of output and combined with a highly efficient optical system capable of zooming from 5,4° to 56°, this unit can easily work as beam or wash light.\nThe Jet Wash7's colour mixing system features precise and advanced control with superior white and saturated tones, and a clean and intuitive user interface similar to the other series.",
